软件包 prefuse.data.query

Dynamic query bindings and data range models for creating dynamic queries.

类摘要
DynamicQueryBinding Abstract base class for dynamic query bindings, which support data queries that can be dynamically edited with direct manipulation user interface components.
ListModel List data model supporting both data modeling and selection management.
ListQueryBinding DynamicQueryBinding supporting queries based on a list of included data values.
NumberRangeModel Range model for numerical data.
ObjectRangeModel Supports an ordered range of arbitrary objects.
RangeQueryBinding DynamicQueryBinding supporting queries based on a range of included data values.
SearchQueryBinding DynamicQueryBinding supporting text search over data values.
 

软件包 prefuse.data.query 的描述

Dynamic query bindings and data range models for creating dynamic queries. A dynamic query binding takes a particular data column and creates a binding between a filtering predicate over the data and user interface widgets for controlling the parameters of the predicate. This includes queries over a range of data (RangeQueryBinding), selecting between different categories of data (ListQueryBinding), and text search (SearchQueryBinding).
